Fvwm is a powerful window manager.  Version 2.5.12 is an alpha
release that includes a few new features and fixes a bug with
window styles and window states that was introduced in 2.5.11.
You are welcome to upgrade and test the new features or help
stabilizing the code. Please be aware that any features introduced
in the 2.5.x development versions may be renamed, changed or
removed without notice before 2.6.0.

This release is available at the home page: http://www.fvwm.org/.

New features:
-------------

* New core features:

   - New command EdgeLeaveCommand.

* New module features:

   - FvwmIconMan: ShowOnlyFocused option.

Bug Fixes:
----------

* Changing a style no longer clears the window state flags defined
  with the State command.
